${project.name}

 A modern HTML5/CSS3 skin for Maven project site generation, based on the
 {{{http://foundation.zurb.com}Foundation}} fluid layout framework. This skin
 allows for proper rendering on desktop computers, tablets and on mobile 
 devices.
 
 <<Your Maven project documentation never looked so good, with so little 
 effort.>>
 
* Getting started

 Add the following skin configuration to your <<<site.xml>>> definition and 
 you're ready to go.
 
+---
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<project>
  <skin>
    <groupId>com.studiomediatech</groupId>
    <artifactId>maven-fluid-skin</artifactId>
    <version>${project.version}</version>
  </skin>
  <body>
    ...
  </body>
</project>
+---
  
